<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n06055d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n06" href="#n06055d">N06 (VI.B.11)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n06all.htm#n06055d"> 55(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> pourquoi&nbsp;(t)</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Essayez donc d&apos;expliquer &agrave; un bonhomme de cinq ans les merveilles de la photographie, de l&apos;aimantation. Essayez de r&eacute;pondre &agrave; ses <mark>&ldquo;pourquoi&rdquo;</mark>... Apr&egrave;s quatre ou cinq exp&eacute;riences, quand le &ldquo;jouet instructif&rdquo; sera fauss&eacute; ou bris&eacute;, le mioche avouera que le moindre poupard e&ucirc;t mieux fait son affaire. <font color="green">[Try to explain to a man of five years the wonders of photography, magnetization. Try to answer his "why" ... After four or five experiments, when the "educational toy" will be skewed or broken, the ugly will admit that the smallest poupard would have done better.]</font> <small> Fr&eacute;d&eacute;ric Queyrat, <a name="FQLJ" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#FQLJ"><cite title="source">Les Jeux des Enfants</cite></a> (1920) 141</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
